{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e21c23c4dc","title":"工农兵诗选","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ac6eccc159","index":0,"year":1966,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"e21c23c4dc"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"b4980847-3787-4b09-b95f-d4bc32199051","name":"红旗一九六六年第五期","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"《红旗》杂志编辑部","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives2/main/b4980847-3787-4b09-b95f-d4bc32199051.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"1cd972bdac","name":"梅茂亭"},{"id":"2f83254f04","name":"殷光兰"},{"id":"63792a03eb","name":"薛治本"},{"id":"cefea3033f","name":"郭国栋"}]},"publication_details":{"b4980847-3787-4b09-b95f-d4bc32199051":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b248022e50","type":"paragraph","text":"工安宾诗选人把毛主席著作比太阳","index":0,"publicationId":"b4980847-3787-4b09-b95f-d4bc32199051","articleId":"e21c23c4dc"},{"id":"b8ca72da6a","type":"paragraph","text":"梅远亭人把毛主席著作比太阳我说太阳比不上太阳上山叉下山毛主席著作日夜放光芒。我士最爱毛主席的书","index":1,"publicationId":"b4980847-3787-4b09-b95f-d4bc32199051","articleId":"e21c23c4dc"},{"id":"af549d2eeb","type":"paragraph","text":"薛治本世界上书籍千千万，毛主席的书战士最爱念。篇篇文章是真理，字字句句金不换。一天不看毛主席的书，饭到嘴里无油盐。天天都念毛主席的书，一颗红心永不变！","index":2,"publicationId":"b4980847-3787-4b09-b95f-d4bc32199051","articleId":"e21c23c4dc"},{"id":"bdf2c39e6d","type":"paragraph","text":"（录白1966年3月31日《解放军报》）不靠神仙不靠天","index":3,"publicationId":"b4980847-3787-4b09-b95f-d4bc32199051","articleId":"e21c23c4dc"},{"id":"82218269d5","type":"paragraph","text":"殿光兰不靠神仙不靠天，集体力量大无边，毛主席带着响办公社","index":4,"publicationId":"b4980847-3787-4b09-b95f-d4bc32199051","articleId":"e21c23c4dc"},{"id":"c85e4817f7","type":"paragraph","text":"换地又改天！1966年第5期景","index":5,"publicationId":"b4980847-3787-4b09-b95f-d4bc32199051","articleId":"e21c23c4dc"},{"id":"3eac1fcd9a","type":"paragraph","text":"郭国栋早晨，勘察队员散坐在旁，吸着清新的空气，阅读毛主席的文章。一句·…··一滴雨露，滋润人们的思想；一篇·一一阵春风，吹开心灵的门窗。身在江边，胸中翻腾着五大洲的风浪脚踏高山，双手描绘着共产主义的图样。满怀激情读着智慧的文章，越读越觉眼明心亮字里行问充满着真理给人们增添力量。太阳照耀着山头的白云，露珠在青草上闪光勘察队员捧着毛主席著作，要把真理的阶梯攀上。","index":6,"publicationId":"b4980847-3787-4b09-b95f-d4bc32199051","articleId":"e21c23c4dc"},{"id":"a9df797172","type":"paragraph","text":"（总271）53","index":7,"publicationId":"b4980847-3787-4b09-b95f-d4bc32199051","articleId":"e21c23c4dc"}],"page":{"id":"04aa32c3ff","publicationId":"b4980847-3787-4b09-b95f-d4bc32199051","articleId":"e21c23c4dc","start":55,"end":55}}}},"__N_SSG":true}